Perquisites:
    - gnu-make
    - gnu-tools
    - clang (used in bindgen)
    - zig (toolchain for cross compiling)
    - odin
    - 7z (7-Zip)
    - fd (find replacement)
    - java 17 (+env JAVA_HOME) [NOTE: this is the one used by android ATM 22/05/2025]
    - android NDK (+env ANDROID_NDK_HOME)
    - android SDK (+env ANDROID_SDK_HOME):
        * build-tools
        * cmdline-tools
        * emulator
        * platform-tools
        * platforms/android-$API

Layout:
    - os:   platform package.
    - game: game/engine package.
    - msic: utils.

